data.description: Great Investment Opportunity! This 1 bedroom 1 bathroom brick ranch is in need of a new owner. Home features large living room, and spacious bedroom. There is a built-in 1 car garage underneath with a partial basement with plenty of storage space. The home needs updated and would make a great rental property or perfect for someone looking to downsize. Located just a couple blocks from downtown Versailles. Don't miss your chance on this great property.
